  "instructions": [
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together lime juice, olive oil, smoked paprika, cumin, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the shredded mexican pibil to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Heat a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
